{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.680", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.280", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.280", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit der heutigen Konstituierung nimmt der Deutsche Bundestag zum 19.\u00a0Mal seine Arbeit auf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.680", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er ist die wichtigste Institution im Parlamentarismus in Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.440", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und er ist zugleich die Herzkammer unserer Demokratie; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.120", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn nur wir Abgeordneten sind vom Volk gew\u00e4hlt und damit unmittelbar legitimiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.160", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Haus debattieren wir \u00fcber die besten politischen L\u00f6sungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.760", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "streiten um die besten Argumente und ringen um Mehrheiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.880", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle vier Jahre tun wir das in Wahlk\u00e4mpfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.560", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dazwischen aber hier. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.280", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Debatten im Bundestag sind daher das Thermometer f\u00fcr die Lebendigkeit unserer Demokratie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.680", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.280", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sich die B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger in unseren Debatten wiederfinden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.800", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "identifizieren sie sich auch mit unserem Parlament. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "72.440", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn aber am K\u00fcchentisch zu Hause oder am Stammtisch heftige politische Diskussionen stattfinden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "72.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.400", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich im Bundestag so nicht wiederfinden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann verlieren wir als Abgeordnete unseren R\u00fcckhalt in der Bev\u00f6lkerung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.480", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbstkritisch f\u00fcge ich hinzu: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.880", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war durchaus in den letzten Jahren der Fall und muss sich dringend \u00e4ndern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.200", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bundestag muss wieder zur zentralen B\u00fchne der politischen Auseinandersetzung werden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.400", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und nicht Talkshows im Fernsehen oder Einzelinterviews von Journalisten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.840", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Bundeskanzlerin."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.800", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Politikstil, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.960", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Merkel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.640", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist ein Grund daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir heute eine rechtspopulistische Partei hier im Bundestag haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.920", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben in diesem Wahlkampf jeden politischen Streit um die besseren Ideen und Konzepte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.640", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "jede Debatte um die besten Argumente verweigert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.720", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Vernebelungsstrategie mag in den vergangenen beiden Wahlk\u00e4mpfen funktioniert haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.400", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesmal f\u00fchrte sie aber dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.520", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die politischen R\u00e4nder st\u00e4rker wurden denn je."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.560", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.520", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss der Bundestag wieder lebendiger werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.320", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er braucht keine Regierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.040", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um zu arbeiten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Gegenteil: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.960", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir halten uns eine Regierung\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber er braucht Regeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.840", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die wir uns hier mit der gleich zu beschlie\u00dfenden Gesch\u00e4ftsordnung selbst geben werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.600", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Regeln m\u00fcssen dem Anspruch des Parlaments, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.640", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Herzkammer der Demokratie zu sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.840", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gerecht werden und diesen auch abbilden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.400", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass diese Regeln reformbed\u00fcrftig sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.320", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist nicht neu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daran haben wir bereits in der vergangenen Legislaturperiode gearbeitet und waren uns auch in vielen Punkten einig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.080", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gleichwohl hat Ihre Fraktion, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.960", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Bundeskanzlerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Union\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.120", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man denn noch von einer Union sprechen kann\u00a0\u2013,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.640", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am Ende eine Einigung blockiert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.840", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Doch wir wollen heute nach vorne schauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.960", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb beantragen wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.080", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Frau Bundeskanzlerin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.600", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so sie denn im Bundestag gew\u00e4hlt wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.240", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich viermal im Jahr einer direkten Befragung im Parlament stellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.600", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viermal im Jahr ist nicht zu viel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.120", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.720", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eigentlich eine Selbstverst\u00e4ndlichkeit\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.000", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen selbst festlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.280", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wozu wir die Regierung in der Regierungsbefragung befragen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.040", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dagegen kann doch niemand sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.760", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ohne die Blockade der Union in der letzten Legislatur h\u00e4tten wir diese Meilensteine schon l\u00e4ngst beschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.640", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich gebe zu: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.640", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir waren an einen Koalitionsvertrag gebunden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.960", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.800", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Union das verhindert hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.520", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir das nicht beschlie\u00dfen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.640", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Selbstkritik geh\u00f6rt dazu."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.040", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben jetzt allerdings keinen Koalitionsvertrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.880", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oder haben wir den schon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.880", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.280", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir geben uns heute hier eine Gesch\u00e4ftsordnung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.400", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in freier Entscheidung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.720", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Sie haben die M\u00f6glichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.600", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "heute frei dar\u00fcber zu entscheiden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.840", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Springen Sie auch!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.040", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Machen wir heute einen Neustart, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.240", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und geben wir uns Regeln, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.200", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das Parlament st\u00e4rken!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.560", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Bundestag hat mehr Kompetenzen als die meisten anderen Parlamente in Europa. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.240", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen schauen auch viele in Europa auf uns. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.200", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei unseren Kompetenzen sind wir Vorbild. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.480", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Art und Weise, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.880", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir hier debattieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.120", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir noch besser werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.160", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.720", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Wort hat jetzt der Kollege Dr.\u00a0Bernd Baumann von der AfD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}